      <para id="id354491">The invertibility of <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mi>X</m:mi><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>z</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:math> is equivalent to the invertibility of</para>
