        <para id="id357307">Hence from Lemma <link target-id="cid6">"Linear Phase Filter Banks"</link><m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>z</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> of unitary filter banks with
PCS symmetry can be parameterized as follows:</para>
        <para id="id357341"><emphasis effect="bold">Theorem 51</emphasis><emphasis effect="italics"> <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>z</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> forms an order <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>K</m:mi></m:math>, unitary filter bank with PCS symmetry iff</emphasis></para><equation id="uid295">
          <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
            <m:mrow>
              <m:msub>
                <m:mi>H</m:mi>
                <m:mi>p</m:mi>
              </m:msub>
              <m:mrow>
                <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                <m:mo>)</m:mo>
              </m:mrow>
              <m:mo>=</m:mo>
              <m:mfenced separators="" open="[" close="]">
                <m:mtable>
                  <m:mtr>
