        <para id="id357615"><emphasis effect="italics">where <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mfenced separators="" open="[" close="]"><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:msub><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mi>i</m:mi></m:msub></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:msub><m:mi>B</m:mi><m:mi>i</m:mi></m:msub></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:msub><m:mi>B</m:mi><m:mi>i</m:mi></m:msub></m:mrow></m:mtd><m:mtd><m:msub><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mi>i</m:mi></m:msub></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable></m:mfenced></m:math> are constant orthogonal matrices. <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>z</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> is characterized by <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mi>K</m:mi><m:mfenced separators="" open="(" close=")"><m:mspace width="-5.0pt"/><m:mtable><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mrow><m:mi>M</m:mi><m:mo>/</m:mo><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mrow></m:mtd></m:mtr><m:mtr><m:mtd><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mtd></m:mtr></m:mtable><m:mspace width="-5.0pt"/></m:mfenced></m:mrow></m:math> parameters.</emphasis></para></section>
      <section id="uid296">
        <title>Characterization of Unitary <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>H</m:mi><m:mi>p</m:mi></m:msub><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mi>z</m:mi><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math> — Linear-Phase Symmetry</title>
        <para id="id357772">For the linear-phase case,</para>
        <equation id="id357776">
          <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
            <m:mtable displaystyle="true">
              <m:mtr>
                <m:mtd columnalign="right">
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:msub>
                      <m:mi>H</m:mi>
                      <m:mi>p</m:mi>
                    </m:msub>
                    <m:mrow>
                      <m:mo>(</m:mo>
                      <m:mi>z</m:mi>
                      <m:mo>)</m:mo>
                    </m:mrow>
                  </m:mrow>
                </m:mtd>
                <m:mtd>
                  <m:mo>=</m:mo>
                </m:mtd>
                <m:mtd columnalign="left">
                  <m:mrow>
                    <m:mi>Q</m:mi>
                    <m:mfenced separators="" open="[" close="]">
                      <m:mtable>
                        <m:mtr>
                          <m:mtd>
                            <m:mrow>
                              <m:msub>
