The <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:math> bands are the <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:math>-point Discrete Fourier Transform bands
as shown in <link target-id="uid311"/>.</para><equation id="uid310">
