      <para id="id366475">then each of the factors <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:msub><m:mi mathvariant="bold">T</m:mi><m:mi>i</m:mi></m:msub></m:math> is a square unitary matrix of size <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mi>L</m:mi><m:mo>-</m:mo><m:mi>N</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mi>M</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math>
and</para>
      <equation id="uid327">
        <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
          <m:mrow>
            <m:munderover>
              <m:mo>∏</m:mo>
              <m:mrow>
