      <para id="id367256">The rows of <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi mathvariant="bold">U</m:mi></m:math> and <m:math overflow="scroll"><m:mi mathvariant="bold">W</m:mi></m:math> form the entry
and exit filters respectively. Clearly they are nonunique.
The input/output behavior is captured in</para>
      <equation id="uid331">
        <m:math overflow="scroll" mode="display">
          <m:mrow>
            <m:mfenced separators="" open="[" close="]">
